# Testing Conventions

## Unit / component (Vitest)

- Colocate: `*.test.ts` / `*.test.tsx` next to source
- Use `@testing-library/react` for components; mock modules with `vi.mock`
- See `src/utils/request.test.ts`, `src/components/app/AppButton.test.tsx` for patterns

```bash
pnpm test                    # all unit tests
pnpm test src/utils/request.test.ts  # one file
```

## E2E (Playwright)

- Specs in `e2e/` (e.g. `e2e/auth.spec.ts`)
- CI runs Chromium with secrets `E2E_USERNAME`, `E2E_PASSWORD`

```bash
pnpm test:e2e
pnpm test:e2e:ui             # debug UI
```

## Blackbox principle

Fix production bugs first. Do not weaken tests to hide failures. See `failing-tests-debugging.mdc`.
